node.title: Police release name of dead Porirua man as investigations continue
node.description: A man who died in suspicious circumstances in Titahi Bay, Porirua, has been named by police as Barry Hall.
node.content:
["A man who died in suspicious circumstances in Titahi Bay, Porirua, has been named by police as Barry Hall.", "", "
File image. Photo: RNZ / Angus Dreaver
", "Police are continuing to investigate how Hall, 44, died at an address in Owhiti Street on 7 July.", "A post mortem examination was completed yesterday and police said the death was still being treated as suspicious.", "Anyone who saw anything unusual in the area at the time is asked to contact police on 105 or anonymously through Crime Stoppers on 0800 555 111."]
